Class WuPalmerComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.similarity.algorithms.api.TermSimilarityMeasureBase
      • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.similarity.algorithms.api.TextSimilarityMeasureBase

            • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.similarity.algorithms.lsr.path.WuPalmerComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SimilarityMeasure, TermSimilarityMeasure, TextSimilarityMeasure

    public class WuPalmerComparator
extends PathBasedComparator
    Implements the relatedness measure by Wu Palmer et al. (1994). wp(c1,c2) = 2 * depth(lcs(c1,c2)) / ( pl(c1,lcs(c1,c2)) + pl(c2,lcs(c1,c2)) + 2 * depth(lcs(c1,c2)) ) pl() is measured in nodes.
    Author:
    zesch
